Starting the project:
---------------------
mvn clean install -Pstart-benchmark

Starting the project using a different mongo host:
--------------------------------------------------
mvn clean install -Pstart-benchmark -Dmongo.config.host=127.0.0.1

Running tests:
-------------
mvn clean install -Dskip.automationtests=false

Install lombok plugin for IDEs:
-------------------------------

Follow the instructions here http://jnb.ociweb.com/jnb/jnbJan2010.html to install lombok plugin for IDEs.